  <section class="beyond-section">
    <div class="beyond-section__inner">
      <div class="beyond-section__content">
        <span class="beyond-section__label">Peleng Island</span>
        <h2>Lake Paisupok & the Jellyfish Lagoon</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Paisupok Lake</strong> is shocking-the water is so clear you can
          see logs fifty feet down. The color is a deep, impossible turquoise. Rent
          a canoe (30k IDR) to find silence away from the dock. Go on a weekday to
          avoid crowds.
        </p>
        <p>
          Rent a scooter (100k IDR) to explore the coast east of Luk Panenteng.
          The road is rough, passing fishing hamlets and coves. Be warned: high
          tide often brings plastic waste-a heartbreaking reality here.
        </p>
        <p>
          Nearby <strong>Paisubatango</strong> is a lagoon filled with stingless jellyfish.
          A farmer guides you through cocoa trees to find it. Don't wear sunscreen.
          Also check out <strong>Paisu Pok</strong>, a chilly cave pool. Back at
          the homestay, expect erratic power and dinner by headlamp.
        </p>
        <div class="beyond-section__highlights">
          <div class="beyond-section__highlight">
            <div class="beyond-section__highlight-title">Paisupok Lake</div>
            <div class="beyond-section__highlight-text">
              Early morning canoe; avoid weekends for serenity
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="beyond-section__highlight">
            <div class="beyond-section__highlight-title">Paisubatango</div>
            <div class="beyond-section__highlight-text">
              Stingless jellyfish lagoon; no sunscreen
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="beyond-section__highlight">
            <div class="beyond-section__highlight-title">Paisu Pok</div>
            <div class="beyond-section__highlight-text">
              Freshwater cave pool; cold and quiet
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
