            <span class="region-card__label">Balut</span>
            <h3 class="region-card__title">Banggai Island</h3>
            <p class="region-card__desc">
              Further south and east. The historical center of the Banggai
              Kingdom. Feels more maritime, denser, and culturally distinct.
