          <p>
            <strong>Jan-Feb (Risky):</strong> Monsoon winds make crossings dangerous
            or impossible. Avoid unless you have flexible dates.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Good to Know:</strong> Lake Paisupok is always clear, but ocean
            visibility drops in rain. During <strong>Ramadan</strong>, day
